      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, which has been meticulously maintained to ensure both mechanical excellence and aesthetic integrity. This unit has successfully undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection, confirming its robust performance capabilities and long-term reliability. With a refined interior and a sophisticated exterior profile, this vehicle represents an ideal acquisition for the discerning driver who prioritizes proven quality and enduring value. Experience a seamless fusion of luxury and utility in a package that stands as a testament to conscientious ownership.",
      "price": 36850.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and still runs like a total dream! It's been well-loved and taken care of, making it the perfect reliable daily driver for its next owner. I\u2019ve had some great memories in this car, but it\u2019s ready for a new adventure. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re really going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L V8, an engine characterized by its individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, this chassis delivers a pure, analog driving experience. The mechanical state is excellent, with documented rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators\u2014essential preventative maintenance for this platform. The factory Electronic Damper Control (EDC) remains fully functional, allowing for precise adjustment of the suspension's compression and rebound characteristics. While the car exhibits minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain is robust, and the subframe has been inspected for structural integrity. A mechanically sound example of BMW's last naturally aspirated M-car.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well maintained. Clean title. No mechanical issues. Cash only.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably dependable and well-cared-for vehicle that strikes the ideal balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a brilliant shine, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear quarter panel\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed but respected. Inside, the cabin remains smoke-free and inviting; the leather upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all interior electronics, from the intuitive infotainment system to the heated seats, operate perfectly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent fluid flush and a fresh set of filters. The engine idles smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp and seamless. The tires are high-quality all-seasons with plenty of life left, and the brakes were recently inspected and found to be in great shape. This is a solid, honest car with a clean title, ready for its next owner to drive home with confidence.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a superior blend of performance and sophisticated styling. Each component has been thoroughly vetted to ensure continued reliability and peak operational efficiency. This remains a premier choice for those who demand excellence and a seamless ownership experience. Inquire today to secure this distinguished asset.",
      "price": 34500.0,
