    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable set of wheels that's ready for its next big adventure? This car has been so good to me and still runs like an absolute dream. It\u2019s been well-loved and maintained, so it's in really solid shape for its next owner. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this ride is ready to go! I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019d love for it to find a great new home. Come on by and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it drives!",
      "price": 32000.0,
